<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 09:13:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国表示所有努力都应在俄乌和平措施中得到认可</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-all-efforts-should-be-recognised-russia-ukraine-peace-measures-2024-06-03/</link><description>中国外交部发言人周一表示，中方认为，支持围绕俄乌战争采取和平措施的一切努力都应得到认可。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 08:22:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/china-says-all-efforts-should-be-recognised-russia-ukraine-peace-measures-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>腾讯、腾讯音乐拟7000万美元入股泰国GMM音乐10%股权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-tencent-music-value-thailands-gmm-music-700-mln-with-stake-buy-2024-06-03/</link><description>泰国娱乐平台GMM Music周一表示，腾讯和腾讯音乐娱乐将以7000万美元收购该公司10%的股份，巩固其分拆计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 06:28:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/tencent-tencent-music-value-thailands-gmm-music-700-mln-with-stake-buy-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>继中国之后，Zara 将直播购物实验扩展到欧洲和美国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/after-china-zara-expands-live-shopping-experiment-europe-us-2024-06-03/</link><description>Zara今年将把直播购物扩展到英国、欧洲和美国，测试一种在中国已经广受欢迎但西方购物者不太熟悉的模式。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 05:10:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/after-china-zara-expands-live-shopping-experiment-europe-us-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：工厂繁忙，市场情绪乐观</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-03/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 04:35:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>由于全球需求强劲，5 月份亚洲工厂活动有所扩大</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asian-factory-activity-expands-may-robust-global-demand-2024-06-03/</link><description>周一的私人调查显示，随着制造商受益于全球需求的扩大，亚洲工厂活动在 5 月份有所扩大，这增加了该地区经济持续复苏的希望，而中国正在显示出反弹的早期迹象。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 03:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-economy-asian-factory-activity-expands-may-robust-global-demand-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟专员表示，欧盟提议的俄罗斯液化天然气转运禁令不会给亚洲带来任何问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/proposed-eu-ban-russian-lng-transhipments-pose-no-problems-asia-eu-commissioner-2024-06-03/</link><description>欧盟能源委员卡德里·西姆森周一在东京对记者表示，针对俄罗斯液化天然气（LNG）转运的欧洲新制裁提议不太可能影响亚洲买家。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/proposed-eu-ban-russian-lng-transhipments-pose-no-problems-asia-eu-commissioner-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度莫迪计划大选后改革以与中国制造业竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-rival-chinese-manufacturing-2024-06-03/</link><description>据两名知情政府官员透露，如果印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪本周赢得第三个任期，他计划采取一系列有利于商业的措施，包括推动制定法规，使雇用和解雇工人变得更容易。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 02:04:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-modi-plans-post-election-reforms-rival-chinese-manufacturing-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>财新PMI显示中国制造业激增，但全球风险增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-growth-hits-2-year-high-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-03/</link><description>周一的一项私营部门调查显示，由于产量增长和新订单，特别是小型企业的新订单，中国5月份工厂活动增长约两年来最快，提振了第二季度的前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:49:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-factory-activity-growth-hits-2-year-high-caixin-pmi-shows-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>交易员思考美联储前景，美元走高；关注欧洲央行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-cautiously-after-us-inflation-report-focus-ecb-2024-06-03/</link><description>美元周一保持稳定，因投资者认为美国通胀可能已放缓至足以让美联储在 2024 年降息，而欧元在欧洲央行本周预期降息之前保持平静。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:37:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/currencies-tread-cautiously-after-us-inflation-report-focus-ecb-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲股市上涨，关注欧洲央行利率变动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-03/</link><description>欧洲股市周一反弹，政府债券收益率下跌，因投资者期待欧洲央行(ECB)降息，而美国就业数据仍将焦点集中在通胀上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 00:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国称英国军情六处将两名中国政府工作人员变成间谍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-britains-mi6-turned-two-chinese-govt-staff-spies-2024-06-02/</link><description>中国国家安全部周一在一份声明中表示，中国指控英国秘密情报局军情六处将两名未透露姓名的中国中央国家机关工作人员变成英国政府的间谍。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 23:38:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-says-britains-mi6-turned-two-chinese-govt-staff-spies-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>尽管市场复苏，繁文缛节仍阻碍中国境外IPO管道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/red-tape-clogs-chinas-offshore-ipo-pipeline-even-markets-recover-2024-06-02/</link><description>银行家、中国公司高管及其投资者表示，他们预计今年离岸IPO荒将持续，在经济放缓的情况下，企业筹集资金的能力将受到影响。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 23:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/red-tape-clogs-chinas-offshore-ipo-pipeline-even-markets-recover-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：PMI盛典开启新月，聚焦中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-02/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 21:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>据天空电视台报道，时装公司 Shein 将在伦敦提交 500 亿英镑的 IPO 招股说明书</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-fashion-giant-shein-file-prospectus-50-billion-london-float-sky-news-2024-06-02/</link><description>据天空新闻周日报道，在线时尚公司 Shein 正准备在伦敦上市之前向英国金融行为监管局提交招股说明书，以供批准，该公司的估值可能约为 500 亿英镑（合 637 亿美元）。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 19:13:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/online-fashion-giant-shein-file-prospectus-50-billion-london-float-sky-news-2024-06-02/</guid></item><item><title>Nvidia表示下一代AI芯片平台将于2026年推出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-says-its-next-generation-ai-chip-platform-be-rolled-out-2026-2024-06-02/</link><description>Nvidia 首席执行官黄仁勋周日表示，该公司的下一代人工智能 (AI) 芯片平台名为 Rubin，将于 2026 年推出。</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 12:53:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-says-its-next-generation-ai-chip-platform-be-rolled-out-2026-2024-06-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>